title: Set page break for table inside list group header will cause data display error.
description: When setting a page break for a table inside a list group header, it causes a data display error.
OB: The page break for a table inside a list group header is causing a data display error.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
- Insert a list with a group 
- Insert a table into the list group header 
- Set the page break before the table to 'always' 
- Preview the page in a web viewer, HTML, or PDF format.
